#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/os.md:3
msgid ""
"`ptool.os` exposes helpers for reading the current runtime environment and "
"querying basic host-process details."
msgstr "`ptool.os` 提供了一组用于读取当前运行时环境、查询宿主进程基础信息的辅助能力。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/os.md:6
msgid "ptool.os.getenv"
msgstr "ptool.os.getenv"

