#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/os.md:10
msgid ""
"`ptool.os.getenv(name)` returns the current value of an environment variable."
msgstr "`ptool.os.getenv(name)` 返回某个环境变量的当前值。"

