#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/os.md:18
msgid ""
"Reads the current `ptool` runtime environment, including values changed by "
"`ptool.os.setenv(...)` and `ptool.os.unsetenv(...)`."
msgstr ""
"读取当前 `ptool` 运行时环境，其中也包括通过 `ptool.os.setenv(...)` 和 "
"`ptool.os.unsetenv(...)` 修改过的值。"

