#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/os.md:55
msgid ""
"`ptool.os.setenv(name, value)` sets an environment variable in the current "
"`ptool` runtime."
msgstr "`ptool.os.setenv(name, value)` 在当前 `ptool` 运行时中设置环境变量。"

