msgid ""
"This updates the current `ptool` runtime environment, not the parent shell."
msgstr "它修改的是当前 `ptool` 运行时环境，不是父级 shell。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/os.md:64
msgid ""
"Values set here are visible to `ptool.os.getenv(...)`, `ptool.os.env()`, and "
"child processes launched later through `ptool.run(...)`."
msgstr ""
"这里设置的值会反映到 `ptool.os.getenv(...)`、`ptool.os.env()`，以及之后通过 "
"`ptool.run(...)` 启动的子进程中。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/os.md:66
msgid ""
"Raises an error when `name` is empty, contains `=`, or when `value` contains "
